printed decorative plant which, although it does not replace the beauty of a real plant, makes the product look just as good. The product is exactly the same; only the live contents of the package change.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e📌 \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/makermur.com\/pages\/normativa-fitosanitaria\"\u003eCheck MAKER-MUR's phytosanitary policy\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e⚠️ Note: The included plant—real or decorative—is an exclusive complement to the VIDA collection and cannot be exchanged for any other product or monetary compensation.\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MAKER-MUR","offers":[{"title":"💧 Water ·","offer_id":53732377624915,"sku":"VIDA-ELEM-AGUA","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"🌀 Wind","offer_id":53732482711891,"sku":"VIDA-ELEM-VIENTO","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true},{"title":"🔥 Fire","offer_id":53732482744659,"sku":"VIDA-ELEM-FUEGO","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1057\/8965\/3331\/files\/BCO.feae4e05-19e6-44fc-b09f-ed27f2ecc6a4.png?v=1779291624"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1057\/8965\/3331\/collections\/DSC_0008.jpg?v=1774886478","url":"https:\/\/makermur.com\/en\/collections\/vida.oembed","provider":"MAKER-MUR","version":"1.0","type":"link"}